# Workflow Modes & Context Tags (Atomic)
- Main modes: [discuss], [meta], [code], [debug], [docs], [test]
- Combined modes: [code][debug], [discuss][meta], [docs][meta]
- Always specify the mode at the start of a session or task.
- Switch modes as the work phase changes.
- Use modes to filter tasks, logs, insights.
- The AI must update llm_context and attention_marker when switching modes.
- Always log mode switches for automation and analysis.

